  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/670750/extras/3c844c3ffc5c4ae510e29e9fcd179fab.avif?t=1770916357\" width=1200 height=735 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A kaleidoscopic trip through space and time.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>You find yourself stranded in a deserted town. Step through its lone neon doorway and tumble into a shifting web of dream backrooms: no combat, no quests, just pure free form exploration!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/670750/extras/82cb4ad4462a3838746a550d67c422b3.poster.avif?t=1770916357\" width=1170 height=732 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/670750/extras/82cb4ad4462a3838746a550d67c422b3.webm?t=1770916357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/670750/extras/82cb4ad4462a3838746a550d67c422b3.mp4?t=1770916357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ Surreal Worlds to Explore: neon cities, liquid forests, glitchy voids, and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paths That Rearrange: doors reshuffle every run, so no two journeys are alike.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/670750/extras/06d043343c1f61145f5273417dd2919e.poster.avif?t=1770916357\" width=1170 height=732 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/670750/extras/06d043343c1f61145f5273417dd2919e.webm?t=1770916357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/670750/extras/06d043343c1f61145f5273417dd2919e.mp4?t=1770916357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Totally Chill: zero pressure, timers, or enemies; wander at your own pace and headspace.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open from the Start: go anywhere, in any order; curiosity is your only map.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evolving Spaces: some worlds morph over time or when revisiting.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/670750/extras/3f19108ccf8d7498535d352c8e0035d2.poster.avif?t=1770916357\" width=1170 height=732 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/670750/extras/3f19108ccf8d7498535d352c8e0035d2.webm?t=1770916357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/670750/extras/3f19108ccf8d7498535d352c8e0035d2.mp4?t=1770916357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ambient Soundscapes: immersive audio crafted to match each realm.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solo Dev passion Project: made with love, there's some minor bugs and missing conventional features. It's just an endless backrooms to explore.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Enjoy the trip!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/670750/extras/3c844c3ffc5c4ae510e29e9fcd179fab.avif?t=1770916357\" width=1200 height=735 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A kaleidoscopic trip through space and time.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>You find yourself stranded in a deserted town. Step through its lone neon doorway and tumble into a shifting web of dream backrooms: no combat, no quests, just pure free form exploration!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/670750/extras/82cb4ad4462a3838746a550d67c422b3.poster.avif?t=1770916357\" width=1170 height=732 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/670750/extras/82cb4ad4462a3838746a550d67c422b3.webm?t=1770916357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/670750/extras/82cb4ad4462a3838746a550d67c422b3.mp4?t=1770916357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ Surreal Worlds to Explore: neon cities, liquid forests, glitchy voids, and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paths That Rearrange: doors reshuffle every run, so no two journeys are alike.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/670750/extras/06d043343c1f61145f5273417dd2919e.poster.avif?t=1770916357\" width=1170 height=732 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/670750/extras/06d043343c1f61145f5273417dd2919e.webm?t=1770916357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/670750/extras/06d043343c1f61145f5273417dd2919e.mp4?t=1770916357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Totally Chill: zero pressure, timers, or enemies; wander at your own pace and headspace.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open from the Start: go anywhere, in any order; curiosity is your only map.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evolving Spaces: some worlds morph over time or when revisiting.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/670750/extras/3f19108ccf8d7498535d352c8e0035d2.poster.avif?t=1770916357\" width=1170 height=732 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/670750/extras/3f19108ccf8d7498535d352c8e0035d2.webm?t=1770916357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/670750/extras/3f19108ccf8d7498535d352c8e0035d2.mp4?t=1770916357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ambient Soundscapes: immersive audio crafted to match each realm.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solo Dev passion Project: made with love, there's some minor bugs and missing conventional features. It's just an endless backrooms to explore.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Enjoy the trip!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
